SELECT "w2"."id" AS "id" FROM ("Weather" AS "w1") CROSS JOIN "Weather" AS "w2" WHERE "w2"."recordDate" - "w1"."recordDate"=1 AND "w2"."Temperature">"w1"."Temperature"
SELECT "w"."id" AS "id" FROM "weather" AS "w" JOIN "weather" AS "wt" ON "w"."recordDate" - "wt"."recordDate"=1 AND "w"."Temperature">"wt"."Temperature"

SELECT "weath1"."id" FROM ("Weather" AS "weath1") CROSS JOIN "Weather" AS "weath2" WHERE "weath1"."Temperature">"weath2"."Temperature" AND EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM "weath1"."recordDate")-EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM "weath2"."recordDate")=1
SELECT "w2"."id" FROM ("Weather" AS "w1") CROSS JOIN "Weather" AS "w2" WHERE "w2"."recordDate" - "w1"."recordDate"=1 AND "w1"."temperature"<"w2"."temperature" GROUP BY 1
SELECT "w2"."id" AS "id" FROM "weather" AS "w1" JOIN "weather" AS "w2" ON "w2"."recordDate" - "w1"."recordDate"=1 WHERE "w2"."temperature">"w1"."temperature"
SELECT "a"."id" AS "Id" FROM "weather" AS "a" JOIN "weather" AS "b" ON "a"."recordDate" - "b"."recordDate"=1 WHERE "a"."temperature">"b"."temperature"
SELECT "W"."id" FROM "Weather" AS "W" JOIN "Weather" AS "W2" ON "W"."recordDate" - "W2"."recordDate"=1 AND "W"."Temperature">"W2"."Temperature"
SELECT "A"."id" FROM ("Weather" AS "A") CROSS JOIN "Weather" AS "B" WHERE "A"."recordDate" - "B"."recordDate"=1 AND "A"."Temperature">"B"."Temperature"
SELECT "b"."id" FROM ("Weather" AS "a") CROSS JOIN "Weather" AS "b" WHERE "a"."temperature"<"b"."temperature" AND "b"."recordDate" - "a"."recordDate"=1
SELECT "t"."id" FROM "weather" AS "t" JOIN "weather" AS "t_l" ON "t"."recorddate"="t_l"."recorddate" + INTERVAL '1 DAY' AND "t"."temperature">"t_l"."temperature"

SELECT "S"."id" AS "Id" FROM (SELECT "id","Temperature",LAG("Temperature", 1) OVER (ORDER BY "recordDate") AS "previousDayTemp","recordDate" - LAG("recordDate", 1) OVER (ORDER BY "recordDate") AS "datediff" FROM "Weather") AS "S" WHERE "S"."Temperature">"S"."previousDayTemp" AND "S"."previousDayTemp" IS NOT NULL AND "datediff"=1
SELECT "w1"."Id" FROM ("Weather" AS "w1") CROSS JOIN "Weather" AS "w2" WHERE "w1"."recordDate" - "w2"."recordDate"=1 AND "w1"."Temperature">"w2"."Temperature"
SELECT "w2"."id" FROM ("Weather" AS "w1") CROSS JOIN "Weather" AS "w2" WHERE "w2"."recordDate"="w1"."recordDate" + INTERVAL '1 DAY' AND "w2"."temperature">"w1"."temperature"
SELECT "id" FROM "Weather" AS "w1" WHERE "Temperature">ANY (SELECT "Temperature" FROM "Weather" AS "w2" WHERE "w2"."recordDate"="w1"."recordDate" + INTERVAL '-1 DAY')
